## SEO & Metadata

### Structure

- Central helpers in `seo/` (e.g., meta builders and defaults).
- Pages import meta builders; avoid inline tags.

### Guidelines

- Per-route titles and descriptions.
- Open Graph and Twitter tags for shareable pages.
- Consider sitemap generation in CI for content-heavy sites.
